        <div n="949A06E2">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-949A06E2-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A06E2-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A06E2-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">A French gentleman dining with some company on a fast-day, called for some bacon and eggs. The <lb/> rest were very angry, and reproved him for so hainous a sin: whereupon he wrote the following lines <hi rend="italics">extempore</hi>; which are here translated.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-949A06E2-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A06E2-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A06E2-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-949A06E2-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A06E2-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A06E2-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1"><l xml:id="swift-949A06E2-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">P<hi rend="italics">eut on croire avec bon sens,</hi></hi></l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-949A06E2-line-2" n="2">Qu'un lardon le mit en colere,</l><l xml:id="swift-949A06E2-line-3" n="3">Ou, que manger un harang,</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-949A06E2-line-4" n="4">C'est un secret pour luy plaire?</l><l xml:id="swift-949A06E2-line-5" n="5">En sa gloire envelopé</l><l xml:id="swift-949A06E2-line-6" n="6">En sa gloire envelopéSonge t'il bien de nos soupé</l>?<l rend="center" xml:id="swift-949A06E2-line-7" n="7"><lb/>In ENGLISH__<hi rend="display-initial">W</hi>HO can believe with common sense,</l><l xml:id="swift-949A06E2-line-8" n="8">A bacon-slice gives God offence,</l><l xml:id="swift-949A06E2-line-9" n="9">Or how a herring hath a charm</l><l xml:id="swift-949A06E2-line-10" n="10">Almighty vengeance to disarm?</l><l xml:id="swift-949A06E2-line-11" n="11">Wrapt up in majesty divine,</l><l xml:id="swift-949A06E2-line-12" n="12">Does he regard on what we dine?</l></lg>
        </div>
      </div>
